{"tid":2085328,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被逼害嘅黃店老闆心聲 + 你問我答","createTime":"2020-06-29T23:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T01:18:21.000Z","uid":48498,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4494097958176cddbeb6239f2ea866265ab6b2be","tid":2085328,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:11:25.000Z","msg":"大家好，多謝咁多位巴絲比我標題黨呃咗入黎先。<br />\n<br />\n最緊要嘅正視聽先：七一，不見不散。<br />\n一定要宣傳咗先。<br />\n<br />\n之後就係講下點解會開依個Post，<br />\n<br />\n一，眾所周知依家連登五毛熱狗龍蛇混雜，想大家唔好比佢地分化到同知道其實香港係有好多好似我咁，甚至係告急緊嘅黃店依家大概係咩情況。<br />\n<br />\n二，就係小弟自己都有多少壓力想訴下苦同問下大家意見。<br />\n<br />\n三，就係小弟都想依個機會宣傳下黎緊有另一個支持同改善嘅黃色經濟圈計劃。<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，小弟就係香港經營緊一間魔術店嘅，詳情就唔自爆，有一到兩個partners 啦，不過主要話事權都係小弟到嘅。<br />\n<br />\n咁運動發生咗之後我就按自己覺得啱嘅方向做事啦，同其他黃店一樣，無論係前期嘅罷工，文宣，派水，物資等（小店係遊行路線）。到中期直情請咗個被捕手捉翻工添。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lcu8kEy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLcu8kEy.jpg&h=ad960b5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZzvO46e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZzvO46e.jpg&h=0ad64384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實講，運動嘅影響絕對未足夠要我地告急嘅，唔可以話無影響，不過只係損失三到四成左右。<br />\n<br />\n到真係到疫情期間，連課都停埋就令小店連去中小學教班嘅穩定收入都冇埋。欠租欠到收律師信，最後都係靠一眾朋友同熟客撐住。<br />\n<br />\n但錯有錯著嘅係就係喺依段無嘢做嘅期間我同一班愛好者都想為香港同依個運動做多一啲嘢，所以就用我地玩過嘅一啲經驗，技術同人脈整咗一副牌用黎籌款比運動。<br />\n<br />\n自我起底：<br />\n【黃色經濟圈】出咗副屬於香港人嘅啤牌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2016637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2016637</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n咁有賴咁多位手足同巴打支持，我地大概籌到7-8萬左右，仲令到一眾黃店可以賺少少錢，我地又可以捐到錢比被捕嘅手足，亦都賣得曬。<br />\n（之後詳細會再出post交代，因為依家有幾位我地目標幫嘅被捕手足（有份幫手出副牌嘅）比班狗一而再，再而三押後審訊，所以未計得準住）<br />\n<br />\n出完依副牌之後就係問題嘅開端，首先最嚴重嘅就係我地一啲合作開嘅公司同我地割席：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k0Rnp3g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk0Rnp3g.jpg&h=781b44b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原諒殘體，不過有時始終好難避免同大陸廠商有交集，特別係魔術圈子唔係特別大<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/skmq7hp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fskmq7hp.jpg&h=621f8c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都包括一啲台灣嘅朋友仔啦<br />\n<br />\n咁我都奇怪邊度黎得咁快我依副1000副嘅小產品會傳得咁快呢？之後有人send比我原來係有同行嘅藍絲放咗上大陸批鬧同國家認證我地<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/svIPUHxtgGlzZZghNmRl-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FsvIPUHxtgGlzZZghNmRl-A&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CKCfq%2BeyIt6E%2B7HnZU0UyvE%3D&h=11e6b7d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/svIPUHxtgGlzZZghNmRl-A</a><br />\n<br />\n之後仲同場放眏比啲小粉紅翻牆留言同大陸蝗比假單同攻擊添<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qOAK7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qOAK7b.jpg&h=939189e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3X57ma.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3X57ma.jpg&h=0d018be9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PKoT1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PKoT1h.jpg&h=51d200f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能睇到依到，你會問？咁我個傻仔係到呷乜鳩呢？有咩意義呢？<br />\n<br />\n我就想同大家講，肯定唔只我一間黃店會咁樣比人搞，甚至搞得更過份或者已經執咗，所以啲分化同熱狗講嘅人血饅頭，係咪真係咁好食呢？<br />\n<br />\n而另一樣就係，人血饅頭係咁多手足犧牲換黎比我地有資源去繼續為依個運動帶黎資源，我地唔食，唔通應該放係到浪費咩？<br />\n<br />\n好老實，我可能捱到，可能未別捱到下去，不過千祈唔好再比啲分化撚令到自己人都批鬥黃店。黃店無錯係會有唔完美，係會有難食，係會有大意放咗義士嘅肖像上牆，亦都會有藍扮黄嘅。但最終總好過比深藍嘅賺好。<br />\n<br />\n點解對方要日屌夜屌黄色經濟圈？係因為我地做依樣嘢係合法，對方點都咬我地唔入，而更加重要嘅係依樣嘢係有效同有傷害性。<br />\n<br />\n 兄弟爬山，各自努力，有錯同難食可以屌，但係要有分串。唔改善嘅就食過幫櫬過第二間黃店，當全市場都係黄嗰陣市場自然會淘汰佢。"},{"pid":"0212b2e545854dd674ebf020cddb2753b7fd3524","tid":2085328,"uid":48498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:12:54.000Z","msg":"太多字比人cut咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同最後越講越興奮out 咗topic <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以最近經營已經好困難，想問下大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外就係有個構思準備緊，想各位巴打絲打幫手宣傳下同支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係有鑑於之前嗰一千副啤牌已經係本地賣曬，而亦都有本地嘅巴打絲打想支持買唔到同外國（最多係台灣同美國）嘅同路人想支持，我亦都覺得如果真係要擴大黃色經濟圈，唔可以淨係靠香港人嘅錢幫翻香港人，一黎幫唔到幾多同幾耐，二黎就係打破藍絲班仆街嘅塘水滾塘魚論。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地計劃緊係台灣眾籌平台: 「嘖嘖」出一副國際版，<br />\n<br />\n。更新重要事件（國安法）<br />\n。翻譯某啲重點做英文同加張文宣卡講點解要支持香港（Hongkong's today, The world's tomorrow ）<br />\n。改良上一代嘅某啲比人屌嘅位(e.g 字體，顏色)<br />\n。加翻一啲魔術同花切會用得到嘅元素（double backer,, Blank card）<br />\n。籌更多嘅款項幫更加多嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n宣傳完，睇下大家有咩意見同有冇嘢關於黃店，魔術店想知，做下你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4ce80e9638aa1b7d991f8fdc25212fdff52880","tid":2085328,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63876b92a11ceddc1529944605e46886479afdd7","tid":2085328,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:15:35.000Z","msg":"依個post係重開黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係一個被逼害就黎告急嘅黃店老闆，你問我答<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2085305\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2085305</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>建議你轉台重po</blockquote>開咩台啱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我唔係好識將分落邊類<br />\n不過多人睇一定係時事或者創意台<br />\n我諗將標題focus係被逼害黃店老闆心聲/忠告都已經會有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a19bf16e872c1900217f0f54937b40c04f0ba4bc","tid":2085328,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:16:02.000Z","msg":"嘩"},{"pid":"aaac5cb9e3a9af7420600f918e1c014e45eaa3f3","tid":2085328,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a19bf16e872c1900217f0f54937b40c04f0ba4bc","tid":2085328,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:16:02.000Z","msg":"嘩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:23:03.000Z","msg":"巴打嘩緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8588e87c49a827b18483a5aff98fb24e8bf617df","tid":2085328,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SANmGbW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSANmGbW.jpg&h=7dcde245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5200ciC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5200ciC.jpg&h=4caff6ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實據我所知，其他賣緊文宣或者抗爭產品嘅黃店一樣經常受迫害，係睇下唔同程度上咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9c3465f9cbd87a0d0174df49bd0ef24dbc2a6ced","tid":2085328,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b4ce80e9638aa1b7d991f8fdc25212fdff52880","tid":2085328,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:29:22.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b379c96f96dca66a65eecc2b85a1425f9d65e8b","tid":2085328,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:31:58.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n老闆辛苦了。"},{"pid":"89483797587ca5051cdd7c46e7c3c2a825d88993","tid":2085328,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:32:39.000Z","msg":"啱啊，人饅點都會有，手足唔食唔通俾藍終港豬食咩屌"},{"pid":"c690157b5fcb3f469b5f463544a8d02e5ac2bf5c","tid":2085328,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89483797587ca5051cdd7c46e7c3c2a825d88993","tid":2085328,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:32:39.000Z","msg":"啱啊，人饅點都會有，手足唔食唔通俾藍終港豬食咩屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:36:53.000Z","msg":"其實手足犧牲我地先有人血饅頭食去賺更多錢請手足，捐款，做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果連咁都唔食，佢地嘅犧牲係更加不值。當然之前煲底單嘢其實係觀點角度問題，唔應該分化，叫佢地注意下，尊重翻就已經可以，我地一間小店已經就死咁濟，你諗下煲底大裝修同咁大間店都係想人勿忘初衷同支持抗爭。可惜比人spin走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd7c67e84d878d7a031d7f33cecd4ee1a86f49e","tid":2085328,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b379c96f96dca66a65eecc2b85a1425f9d65e8b","tid":2085328,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:31:58.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n老闆辛苦了。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:39:17.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打，好多人比我更辛苦，<br />\n希望大家係要支持曬全部黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3eba634bb7dfe72abb120a6616296f3a66b6db","tid":2085328,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:59:34.000Z","msg":"巴打辛苦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熱狗分化撚我會見一個屌一個"},{"pid":"82e03f95ca3cb7f1ef1bcc277d199ec0e1e2e0eb","tid":2085328,"uid":109433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T00:09:45.000Z","msg":"支持黃店 既然呢啲錢點都要洗<br />\n寧願買黃店 希望黃店可以越做越大 搶返香港市場返黎"},{"pid":"706ecf205d91910054edd4a02a6de3dfc26628de","tid":2085328,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82e03f95ca3cb7f1ef1bcc277d199ec0e1e2e0eb","tid":2085328,"uid":109433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T00:09:45.000Z","msg":"支持黃店 既然呢啲錢點都要洗<br />\n寧願買黃店 希望黃店可以越做越大 搶返香港市場返黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T00:19:00.000Z","msg":"香港市場固然重要，更重要係令全世界知<br />\nHongkong's today,  the world's tomorrow"},{"pid":"a8713f85b7e4ab80a3460707e3339054bfdd72f3","tid":2085328,"uid":48498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c3eba634bb7dfe72abb120a6616296f3a66b6db","tid":2085328,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T23:59:34.000Z","msg":"巴打辛苦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熱狗分化撚我會見一個屌一個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T00:19:31.000Z","msg":"無視佢地就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌佢地都曬力"},{"pid":"60466fafec9f341f45643461e6f578b0a5e2b30b","tid":2085328,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T00:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992ee8bdbb86c0ec89f4c9b0c1ff5dec7803743c","tid":2085328,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T00:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3ddaee33356358edea3a3869de9349b6697b75","tid":2085328,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:18:21.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}